<HEADLINE>
FT  30 OCT 92 / UK Company News: Castle Mill losses up to Pounds 948,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Castle Mill International, the textile and clothing designer, recorded a
pre-tax loss of Pounds 948,000, against Pounds 913,000, for the six months
to June 30.
The outcome included a deficit of Pounds 787,000 (Pounds 529,000) from
discontinued businesses; losses on continuing activities were reduced from
Pounds 384,000 to Pounds 161,000.
Overall turnover fell to Pounds 3.75m (Pounds 4.07m) with continuing
activities contributing Pounds 2.65m (Pounds 2.32m). Losses per share were
7.13p (5.82p).
</TEXT>
