<HEADLINE>
FT  30 OCT 92 / Correction
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
In a story headlined 'Lloyd's drafts in help from outsiders' in yesterday's
FT, reference was made to Mercer Consulting and Mercer Fraser. Both
references should have been to Mercer Management Consulting. We apologise
for the error.
