a net loss of Dollars 25m a year ago.
The small profit came despite an Dollars 80m bill for Hurricane Andrew, the
storm system which left a trail of destruction across southern Florida in
late-August.
The insurer also took a one-time restructuring charge of Dollars 51m as it
